Entry.JapaneseText: さほど複雑な作りではないはずだ。 この登山洞を抜けるのは簡単だろう。
Entry.EnglishText: The Climber's Cavern shouldn't be too convoluted. We should be able to get through without issue.

Entry.JapaneseText: よし、その後は、バルカ行きの船だ！ 待ってろよ、姉貴、クレアさん！
Entry.EnglishText: All right, once we're through here, we get on a boat to Balka! Selena, Claire, wait for us!
